{"lemma":"جَمَلَ","slug":"جَمَلَ","root":"ج.م.ل","root_slug":"ج-م-ل","root_link":"/words/roots/ج-م-ل","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"جَمَل","root":"جمل","pos":"N","occurrence_count":1},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":6,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":9},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n6336"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AC%D9%8E%D9%85%D9%8E%D9%84%D9%8E"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to sum up, to summarize"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of جَمَلَ (jamala) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"plural of جُمْلَة (jumla)","tags":["form-of","plural"]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to be beautiful, to be pretty, to be graceful"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to be handsome, to be comely"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to be appropriate, to be proper, to be suitable"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to make beautiful, to beautify, to embellish, to adorn"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"male camel"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"ellipsis of جَمَل الْيَهُود (jamal al-yahūd, “chameleon; mantis”)","tags":["abbreviation","alt-of","ellipsis"]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"From Proto-West Semitic *gamal-."},"ipa":["/d͡ʒu.mal/","/d͡ʒa.mal/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n6336","headword_ar":"جَمَلَ","root":"jml","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jamolN","text_ar":"جَمْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He collected"},{"kind":"text","text":"[a thing, or things]. (K.) [See also 4.] ―         -b2-  Also, (S, Mgh, K,) aor. and inf. n. as above, (S, Mgh,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He melted"},{"kind":"text","text":"fat; (S, Mgh, K;) and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ajtml","text_ar":"اجتمل","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ajml","text_ar":"اجمل","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (A'Obeyd, S, K:) this last was sometimes used: (S:) the best form is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jamala","text_ar":"جَمَلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Fr, TA:) accord. to Z, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ajtml","text_ar":"اجتمل","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he made the melted grease of fat to drip upon bread, putting it again over the fire."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA. [See"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jamiylN","text_ar":"جَمِيلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".])"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jamalaka A@ll~`hu","text_ar":"جَمَلَكَ ا@للّٰهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"May God melt thee like as fat is melted,"},{"kind":"text","text":"is a form of imprecation mentioned in a trad., as used by a woman. (TA.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jamala Aljamala","text_ar":"جَمَلَ الجَمَلَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He put the he-camel apart from the she-camel that was fit to be covered."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)       -A3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jamula","text_ar":"جَمُلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, Mgh, Msb, K;) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jamila","text_ar":"جَمِلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Msb;) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jamaAlN","text_ar":"جَمَالٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Mgh, Msb, K, *) originally"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jamaAlapN","text_ar":"جَمَالَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Msb;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, beautiful, goodly, comely,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pleasing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, Mgh, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in person,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K,) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"good in action,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"actions,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"behaviour,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, TA,) or also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in moral character:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"elegant,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pretty;"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"delicately,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"minutely, beautiful:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Sb, Msb:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"characterized by much goodness, beauty, goodliness, comeliness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pleasingness, in his mind,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in his person,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in his actions"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"behaviour;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and also,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"characterized by much goodness communicated from him to others."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Er-Rághib, TA.) [See"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jamaAlN","text_ar":"جَمَالٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", below; and see also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jamiylN","text_ar":"جَمِيلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]"}],"source_refs":["K","TA","S","Mgh","Fr","M","Sb","Msb"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}